                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <h2 class="text-xs lg:text-[22px] font-semibold text-white uppercase">Large market opportunity</h2>
                        <p class="text-white/60 text-[10px] lg:text-base capitalize mt-2">The cross-border payments market is a massive and growing market, with a total import size of roughly $1.63 tn from MENA and Latin America. Our target market, which includes businesses that use letters of credit for approximately 33% of their imports, is approximately $538 bn. We are targeting 5% of this serviceable market within the first 4 years, which would yield a market of $26.9 bn. Our expected annual revenue is approximately $807 mn.</p>
